"description" = "Track Hearts scores quickly and easily!

Perfect for anyone who loves playing Hearts, whether you're keeping score for a quick game night or a competitive match.

Features:
• Supports 3–6 players
• Full game history so you can review every round
• Pass direction indicator – left, right, or hold on tight!
• Quick add button to assign the remaining points to a player
• iCloud sync – start a game on your iPhone and continue on your iPad
• Shake to undo the previous round
• Flexible Shoot the Moon rules – subtract 26 points from the shooter or add 26 points to everyone else's score
• Clean, simple design that looks great in portrait or landscape
• Dark Mode support

This app is free, open source, and will never include ads.

I hope you enjoy your next game of Hearts!";
